---
@META
dir: src/app/api/admin
updated: 2026-03-18
files: 0
stack: Next.js 14 Route Handlers, Prisma, NextAuth

@PROCESSES
Chapters: GET /api/admin/chapters → list all | POST → create | PUT /api/admin/chapters/[id] → update | DELETE → remove
Users: GET /api/admin/users → list all | PUT /api/admin/users/[id] → update (toggle admin, edit)
Achievements: GET/POST /api/admin/achievements → list/create badges
Analytics: GET /api/admin/analytics → platform stats (users, completions, XP distribution)
Hackathons: GET/POST /api/admin/hackathons → list/create | GET/PUT/DELETE /api/admin/hackathons/[id] → detail/update/delete

@STANDARDS
- All admin routes start with requireAdmin() check
- Return 401 if not authenticated, 403 if not admin
- Use Prisma for all DB operations

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: @/lib/admin-auth (requireAdmin), @/lib/prisma, @/lib/validation-schemas
external: next/server, next-auth
---
